actualClaimLength().details: Gets the Number of all the Claims created till date.

addClaimVoteCA(uint256,uint256).details: Stores the id of the claim assessor vote given to a claim. Maintains record of all votes given by all the CA to a claim.

params._claimId: Claim Id to which vote has given by the CA.

addClaimVotemember(uint256,uint256).details: Stores the id of the member vote given to a claim. Maintains record of all votes given by all the Members to a claim.

params._claimId: Claim Id to which vote has been given by the Member.

addVote(address,uint256,uint256,int8).details: Add Vote's details of a given claim.

changeDependentContractAddress().details: Iupgradable Interface to update dependent contract address

changeFinalVerdict(uint256,int8).details: Sets the final vote's result(either accepted or declined)of a claim.

params._verdict: 1 if claim is accepted,-1 if declined.

getAllClaimsByAddress(address).details: Gets all Claims created by a user till date.

getAllClaimsByIndex(uint256).details: Gets the Claim's details of given claimid.

getAllVoteLength().details: Gets the count of all votes.

getAllVotesForClaim(uint256).details: Gets Id of all the votes given to a claim.
getAllVotesForClaim(uint256).return: ca id of all the votes given by Claim assessors to a claim.mv id of all the votes given by members to a claim.

getCaClaimVotesToken(uint256).details: Gets the total number of votes cast as Claims assessor for/against a given claim

getClaim(uint256).details: Provides information of a Claim when given its claim id.

getClaimCoverId(uint256).details: Gets cover id of a claim.

getClaimDateUpd(uint256).details: Gets the last update date of a claim.

params._index: claim id = pending claim start + given index

getClaimFromNewStart(uint256,address).return: coverid cover against which claim has been submitted.claimId Claim  Id.voteCA verdict of vote given as a Claim Assessor.  voteMV verdict of vote given as a Member.statusnumber Status of claim.

getClaimLength().details: Calculates number of Claims that are in pending state.
